    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2019 Executive Touring Sedan is the perfect blend of performance and sophisticated comfort. Finished in a deep Obsidian Black Metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the rear passenger door\u2014typical of careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary featuring supple, hand-stitched cream leather upholstery that remains firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All premium electronics, including the panoramic sunroof, 12-speaker surround sound system, and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement performed just 500 miles ago. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, responsive power, paired with a transmission that shifts imperceptibly. The sale includes a complete set of service records, two key fobs, and tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a dependable, high-spec vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with total confidence.",
